  the scaffolding system to allow you to layout grids of images very very easily.  You create a thumbnail set by creating a normal &lt;ul&gt; list element, then assigning the class <code>thumbnails</code> to 
  it.  The thumbnails themselves are normal anchor tags with the thumbnail image placed in side of them, and a class of <code>thumbnail</code> given to the &lt;a&gt; element.
</p>

